{"tid":1862424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［機場出走大陸人暴增］沈旭暉：警方捉「散播抗疫謠言」人 林鄭帶頭散播fake news 應被通緝！","createTime":"2020-02-04T15:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T14:46:02.000Z","uid":221265,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b785071bdc5ad369fcf4ffac36a23882cfe4ad","tid":1862424,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"【#最新抗疫大數據】這位big data手足日以繼夜監察政府數字，發現內地訪客出入境人次不但絕非政府官媒宣傳的所謂「大跌八成」、「又跌九成」，而是已經止跌回升，整體內地訪客入境人次升了1,746 （約15％），回到每日超過15,000人；特別值得注意的是，內地訪客從機場入境人次，更大升超過50% （2,347: 4,649➚ 6,996）。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港警方最新指引，拘捕所謂「散播抗疫謠言」的人，林鄭月娥牽頭散播fake news，應被通緝。<br />\n<br />\n(數字來自入境處官方網站，經議員、記者再三要求，農曆新年假期後數字歷來首次繼續每日更新，令真相無所遁形)<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/3022399151127548/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F3022399151127548%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3ahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=019b825b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/3022399151127548/?d=n</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/04/231852_cb1476b265217c5157517665219f4d7f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F04%2F231852_cb1476b265217c5157517665219f4d7f.png&h=b52ed1ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"208b027c5e2b7825a3fb4717a980cdc449a04087","tid":1862424,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:20:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b6d9c38ab9b770aafd28ca1c7c194c9e12e90740","tid":1862424,"uid":2507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:22:17.000Z","msg":"直接拖出去斬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271fe57cb2031cb30bb1c26c458c60994706d5eb","tid":1862424,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6d9c38ab9b770aafd28ca1c7c194c9e12e9074